==English==
===Noun===
'''spout''' (plual: [[spouts]])
# a [[tube]] through which [[liquid]] is [[poured]] or [[discharged]]
# a [[stream]] of liquid
# the [[mixture]] of [[air]] and [[water]] thrown up from the [[blowhole]] of a [[whale]]

===Verb===
'''to spout''' ([[spouted]], spouted)
# to [[gush]] [[forth]] in a [[stream]]
# to [[speak]] [[tediously]] and at [[length]]

